---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Flight School Cost Calculator (Template Preview) | Flight School Friend"
  description="Estimate your likely flight training budget using local aircraft rates, instructor rates, expected total hours, ground instruction, and other common expenses."
>
  <section class="bg-white max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest border border-slate-200">Template Preview</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">Flight School Cost Calculator</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">Estimate your likely flight training budget using local aircraft rates, instructor rates, expected total hours, ground instruction, supplies, written test costs, checkride fees, and other common expenses.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What this tool will help with:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-slate-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Estimate a realistic training budget</li>
          <li>Compare cost scenarios</li>
          <li>Understand how training pace affects cost</li>
          <li>Avoid planning only around FAA minimum hours</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Inputs this tool may use:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1">
            <li>Aircraft hourly rate</li>
            <li>Instructor hourly rate</li>
            <li>Expected total flight hours</li>
            <li>Ground instruction estimate</li>
            <li>Written test and checkride fees</li>
            <li>Headset, books, supplies, and insurance</li>
            <li>Monthly training budget</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-sky-50">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Example output:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-sky-900 space-y-1 font-medium">
            <li>Estimated total cost</li>
            <li>Estimated monthly cost</li>
            <li>Estimated months to finish</li>
            <li>Budget risk level</li>
            <li>Questions to ask a school</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/tools/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">&larr; Back to Tools</a>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition text-center">Start Here</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
